{
  "pageId": "e735baab-fe9f-4ecb-9944-f340b479572a",
  "lastEditedAt": "2023-08-31T03:28:00.000Z",
  "slug": "button-and-link",
  "properties": {
    "title": "リンクはUI表現か？",
    "date": "2023-08-31T03:22:00.000Z",
    "tags": ["雑記", "HTML", "UI"]
  },
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ButtonとLink、どう実装する？ - Google スライド ",
          "annotations": {}
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1rS7BeO1sqbD9-FGRPkst1TCteXkxvPFlfoQh2fWeEus/edit#slide=id.g23f0f9e1b55_0_185",
          "href": "https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1rS7BeO1sqbD9-FGRPkst1TCteXkxvPFlfoQh2fWeEus/edit#slide=id.g23f0f9e1b55_0_185",
          "annotations": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "これを読んでいて思ったこと",
          "annotations": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Buttonは間違いなくUI表現（Look and Feel）の名称である",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": []
        },
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "しかし、LinkはUI表現の名称か？",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "bulleted_list",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "別の問いで言い換えれば、ButtonとLinkって同レイヤーで並べるものなのか？",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "語義的に考える",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "bulleted_list",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Link: ",
                      "annotations": {}
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "[名][C] つながり",
                      "annotations": {
                        "code": true
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "何かと何かをつなげるもの・つながりそのもの",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "機能っぽい",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "慣例的に考える",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "bulleted_list",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "ところでHTMLの文脈でLinkといえば大きく2種類ある",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "bulleted_list",
                      "items": [
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link",
                              "href": "https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a",
                              "href": "https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "bulleted_list",
                              "items": [
                                {
                                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                                  "text": [
                                    {
                                      "type": "text",
                                      "text": "https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-a-element",
                                      "href": "https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-a-element",
                                      "annotations": {}
                                    }
                                  ],
                                  "children": []
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "linkタグ",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "bulleted_list",
                      "items": [
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": ">現在の文書と外部のリソースとの関係を指定します。",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "headタグの中で使われて見た目を持たないので、明らかにこのLinkはUI表現ではない。",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "aタグはAnchorタグである",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "bulleted_list",
                      "items": [
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "> href属性を用いて、別のウェブページ、ファイル、メールアドレス、同一ページ内の場所、または他の URL へのハイパーリンクを作成します。",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "\"アンカー\" が \"リンクを作成\" する　主語と述語",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "アンカー: 錨",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "bulleted_list",
                              "items": [
                                {
                                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                                  "text": [
                                    {
                                      "type": "text",
                                      "text": "別の点（リソース）との間にリンクを形成するための点を置くのがアンカーの役割",
                                      "annotations": {}
                                    }
                                  ],
                                  "children": []
                                },
                                {
                                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                                  "text": [
                                    {
                                      "type": "text",
                                      "text": "そうするとAnchorというのも機能であり、UI表現ではない",
                                      "annotations": {}
                                    }
                                  ],
                                  "children": [
                                    {
                                      "type": "bulleted_list",
                                      "items": [
                                        {
                                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                                          "text": [
                                            {
                                              "type": "text",
                                              "text": "だって錨の形してないし",
                                              "annotations": {}
                                            }
                                          ],
                                          "children": []
                                        }
                                      ]
                                    }
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "であれば、LinkはUI表現ではなく機能としかいいようがない",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "そもそも「ボタンの見た目のリンク」が存在する以上それはそう",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "じゃあいわゆる\"Link\"って、UI表現としてはなんて呼べるんだ？",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "bulleted_list",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Text Button: 文字だけでフレームを見せないボタン",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "bulleted_list",
                      "items": [
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "https://m2.material.io/components/buttons#text-button",
                              "href": "https://m2.material.io/components/buttons#text-button",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "あくまでボタン（押すUI）ということで押し通す",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "しかしこれではテキスト中にインラインで登場するLinkは表現できていなさそう",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "テキスト中にインラインで登場するLink",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "bulleted_list",
                      "items": [
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "いわゆる「青文字で下線が引かれてカーソルが反応するテキスト」をUI表現上なんと呼ぶのか",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "それは文字色が変わったり下線を引いたり引かなかったりしても通用しないといけない（単にスタイリングの違いなので）",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "じゃあもうそれは Text 以上でも以下でもなくない？",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "インタラクティブなTextというのを一語でいいたい気はする。Intaractable Text（長い）",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "\"Link Text\" あるいは \"Linked Text\" と呼べばいいのか？",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                          "text": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "機能としてリンクを作成しているかどうかは見た目に関係ないので、\"Link Button\" も \"Link Text\" も存在していいはず",
                              "annotations": {}
                            }
                          ],
                          "children": []
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "だとすると、レイヤーが揃った整理はこうなのでは",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "bulleted_list",
              "items": [
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "UI表現: Button / Text",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulleted_list_item",
                  "text": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "機能（振る舞い）: Action / Link (Anchor)",
                      "annotations": {}
                    }
                  ],
                  "children": []
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "url": "/images/button-and-link/02e305b8-b00c-41c6-a11f-c2cce1ce6ccc/Untitled.png",
      "caption": []
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bulleted_list",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "つまりですね、「リンク」っていう言葉のあいまいさ（UI表現を指しているのか機能を指しているのか）が残った状態で会話するから混乱が生まれる",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": []
        },
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "「ボタンみたいなリンク」ではなく、UI表現としてButtonであり発揮する機能がLinkである",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": []
        },
        {
          "type": "bulleted_list_item",
          "text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "いわゆる「リンク」を言いたいときは Link TextやらText Linkなどと読んでみてはどうか",
              "annotations": {}
            }
          ],
          "children": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": []
    }
  ]
}
